hat is really happening in this country. Things dont just happen for no reason; taking prayer out of schools, trying to take the Lords name out of context, making homosexuals acceptable to the American people, and these secular, twisted groups like ACLU and other organizations have a specific goal; to break up our families, because without strong, Christian families and a strong tie to the one who built this nation and was founded upon His name, JESUS CHRIST, America will crumble. Our nation NEEDS God, in our homes, schools, and in our hearts. We cant let these bad people get away with the things that they are doing. If they are driven by satan so as to attack and take the rights away of Gods people, how much more driven should we be, standing firmly on Christs name, to fight the deceiver. Gods voice will not be toned down, but shall we yell it out for all the world to hear! God bless you all. "/><type4:DocumentMetaData xmi:id="13" sofa="1" begin="0" end="1214" language="en" documentId="1778" isLastSegment="false"/><types:WebArgumentMetadata xmi:id="24" sofa="1" begin="0" end="0" author="Jennifer" date="03/22/2011 10:13 PM" docType="artcomment" origUrl="http://www.forerunner.com/forerunner/X0098_Ban_on_school_prayer.html#c002579" topic="prayer-in-schools" thumbsUp="0" thumbsDown="0" origId="1778" notes="" title="Banning Prayer in Public Schools Has Led to America's Demise"/><type6:Paragraph xmi:id="39" sofa="1" begin="0" end="1214"/><cas:View sofa="1" members="13 24 39"/></xmi:XMI>